title: Can Practice tool games show up on your match history?
body:
I've been looking through people's match history, and it seems that it doesn't, but i just need some confirmation.

Thanks.

replies.body: I don't believe it shows up as match history since it's not actually a matchmade game, and the stats it would show could be totally wild and out there.  That's just my thought tough, as I'm not part of the client dev team and don't actually know for sure.  Share your feedback and suggestion to fellow testers and the client devs over at the [client discussion](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/alpha-client-discussion) boards.  Thanks for testing!
